# Online Product Catalog

## Description

An online catalog to add and view products. This app lets you manage a list of products by adding new ones and displaying them with their name, description, price, and availability.

## Features

- Add a new product
- View the list of products
- Displays product details such as name, description, price, and availability

## to access the app

1. Navigate to http://localhost:3000/admin to add a new product.

2. Fill in the form with the product details: name, description, price, and availability.

3. Once you submit the form, you will be redirected to the catalog page (/), where you can view the newly added product.

4. Navigate to http://localhost:3000 to view the list of products.

5. If there are no products, a message saying "No products are available at the moment" will be shown.
